<div class="l-section__row">
<h2 class="c-section__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<div class="c-accordion m-secondary h-text-align-left" data-component="global/Accordion" data-component-options="{ &quot;multiExpand&quot;: false }">

<div itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage">

<!-- START Q&A content block 1 -->
<div class="c-accordion__item " data-js-accordion-item="" itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<div class="c-accordion__title" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="content-1" data-js-accordion-control="" role="button" tabindex="0">

<!-- START QUESTION copy HTML markup -->
<h3 style="font:inherit;" itemprop="name">WHAT IS THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN SQUALANE AND SQUALENE? </h3>
<!-- END QUESTION copy HTML markup -->

</div>

<div class="c-accordion__content" id="content-1" aria-hidden="true" data-js-accordion-container="">

<div class="c-accordion__content-inner" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<!-- START ANSWER copy HTML markup-->
<p>While they are related, Squalane and Squalene are not identical. Squalane is the hydrogenated form of Squalene. Squalene is naturally occurring in our bodies and makes up around 13% of the skin’s sebum, helping to protect the skin’s barrier and seal in moisture. In our moisturizing cream, we derive the same skin benefits from Squalane, which is stable against heat and oxidation making it ideal for skincare formulations.</p>
<!-- END ANSWER copy HTML markup-->

</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- END Q&A content block 1 -->

<!-- START Q&A content block 2 -->
<div class="c-accordion__item " data-js-accordion-item="" itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<div class="c-accordion__title" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="content-2" data-js-accordion-control="" role="button" tabindex="0">

<!-- START QUESTION copy HTML markup -->
<h3 style="font:inherit;" itemprop="name">HOW IS THE SQUALANE IN ULTRA FACIAL CREAM SOURCED?</h3>
<!-- END QUESTION copy HTML markup -->

</div>

<div class="c-accordion__content" id="content-2" aria-hidden="true" data-js-accordion-container="">

<div class="c-accordion__content-inner" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<!-- START ANSWER copy HTML markup-->
<p>Squalane can be derived from several different natural resources. In our moisturizing cream, we use Squalane derived from olives and sugar cane. Kiehl’s never formulates with animal-derived Squalane. </p>
<!-- END ANSWER copy HTML markup-->

</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- END Q&A content block 2 -->

<!-- START Q&A content block 3 -->
<div class="c-accordion__item " data-js-accordion-item="" itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<div class="c-accordion__title" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="content-3" data-js-accordion-control="" role="button" tabindex="0">

<!-- START QUESTION copy HTML markup -->
<h3 style="font:inherit;" itemprop="name">WHAT IS THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN KIEHL’S ULTRA FACIAL CREAM AND MOISTURIZER? </h3>
<!-- END QUESTION copy HTML markup -->

</div>

<div class="c-accordion__content" id="content-3" aria-hidden="true" data-js-accordion-container="">

<div class="c-accordion__content-inner" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<!-- START ANSWER copy HTML markup-->
<p>Ultra Facial Cream with Squalane and Ultra Facial Moisturizer both deliver 24-hour hydration and are formulated with Squalane and Glycerin for hydrated, soft &amp; smooth skin. Ultra Facial Cream with Squalane has a lightweight cream texture ideal for deep all-day hydration on all skin types. Ultra Facial Moisturizer has a thinner formula that absorbs instantly to skin and is ideal for oilier skin types. </p>
<!-- END ANSWER copy HTML markup-->

</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- END Q&A content block 3 -->

<!-- START Q&A content block 4 -->
<div class="c-accordion__item " data-js-accordion-item="" itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<div class="c-accordion__title" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="content-4" data-js-accordion-control="" role="button" tabindex="0">

<!-- START QUESTION copy HTML markup -->
<h3 style="font:inherit;" itemprop="name">WHAT IS THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN ULTRA FACIAL CREAM AND FACIAL FUEL MOISTURIZER? </h3>
<!-- END QUESTION copy HTML markup -->

</div>

<div class="c-accordion__content" id="content-4" aria-hidden="true" data-js-accordion-container="">

<div class="c-accordion__content-inner" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<!-- START ANSWER copy HTML markup-->
<p>Ultra Facial Cream with Squalane is a 24-hour facial cream formulated for all skin types, tones and textures. Formulated with Squalane and Glycerin, our moisturizing cream delivers maximum hydration for soft, smooth skin and is suitable for men. Facial Fuel Energizing Moisturizer is a daily moisturizer formulated with Vitamin C and Caffeine to revitalize men’s unique skin. </p>
<!-- END ANSWER copy HTML markup-->

</div>

</div>
